#: ../../user/changelog.md:37
msgid ""
"Bump GitHub Actions to Node 24 runtimes (checkout v7, setup-node v6, "
"setup-uv v7, upload-pages-artifact v5, deploy-pages v5, upload-artifact "
"v7)."
msgstr ""
"GitHub Actions を Node 24 ランタイムに更新（checkout v7、setup-node v6、setup-uv v7"
"、upload-pages-artifact v5、deploy-pages v5、upload-artifact v7）。"

