#: ../../user/changelog.md:43
msgid ""
"Documentation only: add CI (Docs/Release) and GitHub Sponsors badges to "
"the README. No code changes; the published widget is identical to 0.1.0."
msgstr ""
"ドキュメントのみ: README に CI（Docs/Release）と GitHub Sponsors "
